1bd598f7664a","tid":261762,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T02:39:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點先可以瞬間睇出自己叫幾飛</blockquote><br />\n有冇例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分飛燕就叫頭至尾+1<br />\n3334555<br />\n叫23456咁"},{"pid":"dab9ad6031acb3b78cf3867ea62ad94a8ccf2292","tid":261762,"uid":14350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T02:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8e0a51a1b511d6ffe15bc27eb825167e099332","tid":261762,"uid":90704,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T02:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三番都係運氣主導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三番係最撚悶嘅麻將玩法<br />\n得d無見識嘅on9先會話好玩</blockquote><br />\n你揸死我，我揸死佢<br />\n全部唔好食<br />\n邊個自摸就係旺，三家合作殊死佢<br />\n憎人富貴厭人貧<br />\n暗合中國人文化"},{"pid":"3a6f7ac0e585122a3c7ff2ad6e0cf5b8a8168ed5","tid":261762,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T03:20:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無人打斷幺雀眼平糊，二番起糊打到六番</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhere</blockquote><br />\n搵左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我覺得呢d先考技術，最高境界<br />\n<br />\n以前睇呀媽打覺得唔係咁難，落到場先知咩叫快上快落，識玩章法高先會贏</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄，我好感動除左同屋企人打，街無人識打<br />\n<br />\n班妹下妹下打呢d先高章</blockquote><br />\n玩呢d好難衡量取捨，同三番唔同，三番得個一兩條路，就係混/清一色，同埋對對(仲有咩平糊花自摸呢個on9野)<br />\n<br />\n兩番起六番止，好多決擇要做，潛在變化實在太多，無咁上下功力係絕對handle唔到<br />\n<br />\n三番起嘅變化太少"},{"pid":"5785efe7c2b037433aa5c688eba6f484f16af521","tid":261762,"uid":22463,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T03:25:04.000Z","msg"